            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "@zeertzjq it's an option for $TERM (like xterm-256color) from the research I did, \"ncurses\" or \"terminfo\" are the programs that handle $TERM.\r\nTmux recommends using screen-256color or tmux/tmux-256color.\r\nscreen-256color has the same problem as xterm-256color but also messes up letters I type\r\nOnly certain versions of ncurses support tmux/tmux-256color, and my setup seems to not have a tmux/tmux-256color option available, and I couldn't figure out if there is even a way to \"install\" those options.\r\n",
